titles.title: A bill to suspend temporarily the duty on 3-(a-acetonyl benzyl)-4-hydroxycoumarin sodium salt.

action.text: Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 6/15/1993--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend, through December 31, 1996, the duty on 3-(a-acetonyl benzyl)-4-hydroxycoumarin sodium salt.
